{"tid":2389242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實興趣係咪真係唔應該加入競爭元素呢？","createTime":"2021-01-31T17:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:05:08.000Z","uid":270893,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78aa1d2cc6be82a51102d8f8c6e07a9d93eb700e","tid":2389242,"uid":270893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發覺要同人鬥嘅時候，就不知不覺有好大壓力，然後對嗰項興趣嘅熱情不斷被消減，甚至會有一絲想逃避嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n見過有好多人話希望將興趣變成事業，但你唔怕會因為變成事業之後就開始討厭呢個興趣咩？定其實只係我問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：鍾意踢波打波但完全唔想入校隊，鍾意藝術但無論中學定大學揀科都唔會揀藝術讀，鍾意打機但好討厭要同人哋鬥高分鬥排名"},{"pid":"e895b5911a886d5b48d82d6477c69f74c86ee24f","tid":2389242,"uid":371480,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"失敗者心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487badde7e33bd2f84647239f947fbc65539a074","tid":2389242,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"良性競爭 vs 惡性競爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"7db8e7e0959528842e07533b4ffc317d03b4a1e1","tid":2389242,"uid":270893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487badde7e33bd2f84647239f947fbc65539a074","tid":2389242,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"良性競爭 vs 惡性競爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此post已完"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"但無論邊個都會令我好大壓力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbce6189949c27690379beb3f506138f12817ca","tid":2389242,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7db8e7e0959528842e07533b4ffc317d03b4a1e1","tid":2389242,"uid":270893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487badde7e33bd2f84647239f947fbc65539a074","tid":2389242,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:53:40.000Z